Hundt Wants Creditors to Join Greece Help, Abendblatt Says

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-06-13T07:46:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/hundt-wants-creditors-to-join-greece-help-abendblatt-says.html
Dieter Hundt, president of  Germany ’s
BDA employers’ federation, wants private creditors to
participate in a second bailout package for  Greece , the
 Hamburger Abendblatt  newspaper reported in an e-mailed preview
of a report to be published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net . 